WolfEngine license
==================

WolfEngine does not have a license at this time.

That means that you are permitted to:
- Look at the source code for private use
- Download the source code for private use
- Compile the source code for private use
- Modify the source code for private use

You are not permitted to:
- Redistribute the source code and/or compiled binaries
- Sublicense the source code and/or compiled binaries

You are always permitted to:
- Ask to use the source code under a different license

contact: rvanee@wolfos.org
